## Workflow

This project uses the [Founder Stack](https://github.com/rajconnects/founder-stack) workflow. The five-layer build cycle:

| Layer | Command | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| 1. Intake | `/spec-intake <spec>` | Spec → structured plan |
| 2. Plan | (built-in plan mode) | Approve plan before implementation |
| 3. Execute | (hooks: auto-lint, tsc-check, pre-git-check) | Implementation with rails |
| 4. Verify | `/test-gate`, `/design-gate`, `/schema-gate` | Test-first contract, design audit, DB safety |
| 5. Ship | `/deploy-gate <env>`, `/handoff <phase>` | Smoke check, handoff doc, decision traces |

Full reference: `.claude/Engineering-Playbook.md`

